      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MELLCAT BAD BOY (5) could manage only second at this track last time but impressed when clocking a scintillating 19.51 over 350m at this track the start prior. Rates on top and can find winning form again. LUCKY WINNER (1) had been in great form but missed the frame latest when fifth (23.10) in a Grade 4/5 at Bulli. Normally safely away but always well back and facing a task from wide out last time. Has a good record here at this journey. Better than last start and can bounce back. SILENT ACCORD (3) missed the frame last time but had been racing well prior to that, winning a Grade 5 three back before a placing at this track the following run. Expected to do much better this time. ORSON JIMMY (2) will have admirers after surprising many with a placing last time out.",
